g.title: Setup
g.text: Create a unique workspace and transform the input file to a file
with chosen format and field names standardized to Darwin Core

g.title: FileToDataStream
g.text: Take the darwinized occurrence file and stream records from it

g.title: EnvironmentTagger
g.text: Tag each record in the stream that appears to be marine with isMarine=true and nonmarine with isMarine=false

g.title: FilterToJustMarine
g.text: Pass only records tagged with isMarine=true

g.title: FilterExcludingMarine
g.text: Pass only records not tagged with isMarine=true

g.title: WoRMSLookup
g.text: Lookup GUIDs for names in WoRMS

g.title: GBIFLookup
g.text: Lookup GUIDs for names in GBIF

g.title: CsvFileWriter
g.text: Write to a csv file and wrapup by finishing the workflow
